    v2 = 1.0

    v0 = (wp.abs(v1) * (wp.exp(v1 + 0.60) * wp.abs(v0 + 0.28)))
    v1 = wp.sin(0.77)
    v2 = ((v2 * 0.68) + wp.abs((v1 + 0.11 / v1 + 0.04)))
